items.name: docker-mysql-setup
items.description: This repository provides an all-in-one, cross-platform solution for setting up MySQL in Docker using one-click scripts. It includes easy-to-use installation scripts for Windows, Linux, and macOS, along with a Docker Compose configuration to spin up a MySQL instance effortlessly.

items.name: docker-soketi-setup
items.description: Effortlessly set up a high-performance WebSocket server using Soketi with Docker. This repository includes installation scripts (install.ps1 for Windows and install.sh for Linux/Mac) and a docker-compose configuration to customize and deploy Soketi, integrated with Docker networks for real-time application needs.

items.name: docker-phpmyadmin-setup
items.description: A lightweight solution to deploy phpMyAdmin using Docker. Includes automated scripts to set up a web interface for managing MySQL databases. Features customizable ports, seamless network integration, and environment file support. Ideal for developers and database admins.
